rows.label: tlk4234011301_msg0001
rows.name:
Toatoa is studying history
from salvaged items, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011301_msg0002
rows.name:
No one knows if salvaged items
were actually used in the way
their names suggest, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011301_msg0003
rows.name:
For example, the Giant's Black Ring is
said to be a giant's ring, but... the giant
in question has never been found, mo.

rows.label: tlk4234011301_msg0004
rows.name:
See? Feel the romance,
mo? It's fun, mo!
